title: U-17 World Cup: Chile thrashes the United States 4-1 (CONMEBOL - Confederación Sudamericana de Fútbol) ...
text: ( Source : CONMEBOL - Confederación Sudamericana de Fútbol ) Chile grabbed a come-from-behind 4-1 victory in Vina Del Mar against USA , but the win was not enough to secure second place in Group A due to Croatia 's own heroics against Nigeria .
